ABSTRACT
Techniques for tethering parameters for a tethering connec-
tion are described. Implementations, for example, enable a
tethered connection between a tethered device and a host
device to be provisioned in various ways.
20 Claims, 14 Drawing Sheets
800
Receive a tethering query that includes a location of a host
device and attributes of a requesting device that requests to
tether to the host device
802
Select, based on the location of the host device and attributes of
the requesting device, wireless channels to assign to the host
device for wireless data communication
804
Generate a tethering response that identifies the wireless
channels and tethering parameters to be applied to a tethered
connection between the requesting device and the host device
806
Communicate the tethering response for receipt by the host
device
